Scenario1 : After Submit - All my AMS notifications responded too (completed tick and message)
Given I am logged on as a farmer to BISS
And if I have any Red notifications from AMS
And I see panel
With header AMS findings
And underneath I see AMS status
And I see a red triangle symbol showing my Red notifications, with the label “AMS findings”
And I see a label marked All responses completed with a green tick to the right
And in the amount column, the count remains the same
And If I have rejected any AMS notifications I will see a message in AMS panel on Farmer dashboard – "You have submitted your AMS responses, please respond to any AgriSnap requests promptly"
If i have accepted or withdrawn (not rejected) my AMS notification, i do not see a message
And I see a View Responses button (green)
And when I press it it will take me to the AMS screen
And I will see my parcels and my responses
And the side drawer will not be shown
And I will not see a submit button
I will see a back button, and pagination on the page (if needed)
And If I have rejected any AMS notifications I will see a message top of page blue – "You have submitted your AMS responses, please respond to any AgriSnap requests promptly"

